Schedule: Monday to Friday; position can be based in Val d’Or, Mirabel (Quebec), Rankin Inlet or Baker Lake (Nunavut) with occasional presence at the Kivalliq communities and mine sites in Nunavut. During the COVID-19 pandemic, you will work from home.

